Miscellaneous.name: NMB Media Apps All-In-One Master Panel
Miscellaneous.description: Built upon the beloved NMB Media Apps All-In-One Master Panel v1.0a (Legacy), this successor offers a faster, smoother experience. Crafted from the ground up with a modular design, it's fully customizable to meet users unique needs. Packed with features for owners and users alike, it comes pre-installed with the Multi-service Proxy Module. Plus, enjoy the added versatility of Custom Android WebView Widgets. P.S. This is hosted by myself.
